This pull request has conflicts that need to be resolved before we can go further with it.

An explanation of the change for reviewers: I took the code that creates the Hive stats (and native HBase stats) schema and the histograms tables out of HSGlobalsClass::Initialize and put them in a new method, HSGlobalsClass::InitializeStatsSchema. The former method now calls the latter. I also added a call to the latter to function managePersistentSamples; this function is executed for UPDATE STATISTICS ... CREATE / REMOVE SAMPLE.
